1
00:01:40,670 --> 00:01:46,020
[THE DEVIL BETWEEN US]

2
00:01:46,080 --> 00:01:49,039
[Episode 15]

3
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:50,590
Nie.

4
00:01:50,590 --> 00:01:51,350
Come on, Nie.

5
00:01:51,350 --> 00:01:51,870
Bro.

6
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:53,009
Do me a favor.

7
00:01:53,350 --> 00:01:55,200
I've been standing here for ten minutes.

8
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:56,660
It hasn't been easy for me.

9
00:02:00,580 --> 00:02:01,310
It's simple.

10
00:02:01,380 --> 00:02:03,530
Just check if it contains any drugs.

11
00:02:10,710 --> 00:02:12,440
It won't take much of your time.

12
00:02:15,600 --> 00:02:17,480
What is this junk?

13
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,880
Pills. Just ordinary pills.

14
00:02:20,950 --> 00:02:22,530
I'm going abroad for a trip
in a couple of days.

15
00:02:22,530 --> 00:02:23,800
Please help me ship some goods.

16
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:24,840
It's simple.

17
00:02:25,280 --> 00:02:27,400
I've already arranged everything with
the courier company.

18
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:28,360
Here is a list.

19
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:29,490
Check the items against it.

20
00:02:29,490 --> 00:02:30,470
When the courier arrives,

21
00:02:30,470 --> 00:02:31,800
sign and send them off.

22
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:32,560
That's all.

23
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:33,520
Okay.

24
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:35,220
What do you want to eat?

25
00:02:35,630 --> 00:02:36,630
Anything is fine.

26
00:02:37,490 --> 00:02:38,710
You always said this.

27
00:02:38,710 --> 00:02:39,840
In high school,

28
00:02:40,040 --> 00:02:41,960
whenever I asked what you wanted,
you'd say that.

29
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:43,360
But you can't do it today.

30
00:02:43,430 --> 00:02:45,430
Today is the big day of your new life.

31
00:02:45,460 --> 00:02:46,910
We should eat something good.

32
00:02:46,910 --> 00:02:47,520
Let's go.

33
00:02:48,190 --> 00:02:48,870
Xiaoya.

34
00:02:49,079 --> 00:02:49,910
Wenjing...

35
00:02:53,220 --> 00:02:53,890
What?

36
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:56,670
Are you hiding anything from me?

37
00:02:57,210 --> 00:02:58,240
When she left today,

38
00:02:58,240 --> 00:03:00,500
she took a few bags of pills
from this box.

39
00:03:15,030 --> 00:03:16,030
Wenjing said she gained weight

40
00:03:16,030 --> 00:03:17,100
and wanted to lose some.

41
00:03:17,100 --> 00:03:18,560
It's just a few bags of pills.

42
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:20,360
She can have as many as she wants.

43
00:03:20,760 --> 00:03:21,290
Let's go.

44
00:03:21,460 --> 00:03:22,340
Really?

45
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:32,020
Have you made up your mind?

46
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:35,150
Are you sure you do not want to
hide it somewhere?

47
00:03:35,150 --> 00:03:36,610
What if we come back later?

48
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:11,560
It's a fresh start.

49
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:15,970
I've already booked flights
for four days later.

50
00:04:16,220 --> 00:04:19,399
The money from all the agents
will be transferred to us in three days.

51
00:04:19,399 --> 00:04:21,310
Even if we don't ship to them now,

52
00:04:21,790 --> 00:04:23,380
there's nothing they can do about it.

53
00:04:23,380 --> 00:04:24,700
Why ship fakes?

54
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:26,870
If we don't deliver the goods,

55
00:04:26,870 --> 00:04:29,470
they'll suspect something
as soon as we leave.

56
00:04:29,940 --> 00:04:31,770
But if we can find someone

57
00:04:32,470 --> 00:04:34,240
to leverage the reputation we built

58
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:35,900
and continue shipping fakes,

59
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:38,830
in just one night,

60
00:04:39,500 --> 00:04:40,960
we can make millions more.

61
00:04:42,190 --> 00:04:44,120
That's called maximizing profit.

62
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:48,600
We don't have any drugs now.

63
00:04:48,830 --> 00:04:51,630
Even if the police catch us,
they have no evidence.

64
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:52,440
Xiaoya,

65
00:04:55,130 --> 00:04:56,250
can we stay?

66
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:04,920
Can you guarantee

67
00:05:05,830 --> 00:05:08,830
that the first batch of drugs
we used to open the market

68
00:05:09,950 --> 00:05:11,190
and the samples we gave the agents

69
00:05:11,190 --> 00:05:12,520
have all been consumed?

70
00:05:13,910 --> 00:05:15,310
Can you guarantee Xiaoyu

71
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:17,710
will never be found?

72
00:05:18,750 --> 00:05:20,160
Or can you guarantee that

73
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:23,460
Cheng Ken will
take the fall for everything?

74
00:05:29,090 --> 00:05:29,800
I see.

75
00:05:31,570 --> 00:05:33,210
We have to leave.

76
00:05:35,590 --> 00:05:37,990
At least we managed
to make a graceful exit.

77
00:05:48,270 --> 00:05:49,120
Xiaodong.

78
00:05:49,390 --> 00:05:51,450
I haven't seen you fishing in a while.

79
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:53,480
Yeah, Uncle.

80
00:05:53,550 --> 00:05:54,950
I've been busy lately.

81
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:56,090
That's fine.

82
00:05:56,150 --> 00:05:58,210
It's good for young people to be busy.

83
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:08,430
Uncle,

84
00:06:09,430 --> 00:06:10,560
can your son

85
00:06:11,080 --> 00:06:12,960
help me send two people away?

86
00:06:13,790 --> 00:06:15,350
Time and place.

87
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:18,840
Going to Maide in three days.

88
00:06:19,750 --> 00:06:20,550
In three days?

89
00:06:21,870 --> 00:06:23,000
What a coincidence.

90
00:06:24,190 --> 00:06:25,070
He took an order

91
00:06:25,620 --> 00:06:28,080
to send someone away
the day after tomorrow.

92
00:06:29,420 --> 00:06:30,750
The day after tomorrow?

93
00:06:36,190 --> 00:06:37,520
Is it like my situation?

94
00:06:37,830 --> 00:06:38,390
Yes.

95
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:48,720
So, things between you and Cheng Xiaodong

96
00:06:48,720 --> 00:06:50,270
are good again?

97
00:06:51,130 --> 00:06:52,420
He treats me well.

98
00:06:54,830 --> 00:06:55,630
Why isn't he here yet?

99
00:06:55,630 --> 00:06:56,490
Are you hungry?

100
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:57,000
I'm not hungry.

101
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:58,659
Don't worry. Let's wait a bit.

102
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:00,680
Speak of the devil.

103
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:02,560
I thought you fell into the sea.

104
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:03,390
What's up?

105
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:07,390
Cheng Xiaodong, what are you doing?

106
00:07:07,390 --> 00:07:08,390
Are you crazy?

107
00:07:09,040 --> 00:07:09,720
Let go!

108
00:07:10,310 --> 00:07:11,310
Cheng Xiaodong!

109
00:07:11,390 --> 00:07:12,560
What are you doing?

110
00:07:12,870 --> 00:07:13,430
Let go!

111
00:07:14,600 --> 00:07:15,720
Why did you lie to me?

112
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:16,270
Lie about what?

113
00:07:16,270 --> 00:07:16,950
What do you mean?

114
00:07:16,950 --> 00:07:18,970
You contacted a boat to leave on your own.

115
00:07:18,970 --> 00:07:20,970
You never intended to leave with me.

116
00:07:25,750 --> 00:07:26,510
Xiaodong.

117
00:07:27,350 --> 00:07:28,510
Let's go back and talk.

118
00:07:28,510 --> 00:07:29,190
Not here.

119
00:07:29,270 --> 00:07:30,730
We're talking right here.

120
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:32,310
If you wanted me to stay,

121
00:07:32,310 --> 00:07:33,570
you could have told me.

122
00:07:33,580 --> 00:07:35,550
I can take the fall for you.

123
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:37,190
I can die for you.

124
00:07:37,220 --> 00:07:38,950
I have made all the preparations.

125
00:07:38,950 --> 00:07:40,560
But why did you lie to me?

126
00:07:44,670 --> 00:07:45,600
Let's go outside.

127
00:07:45,600 --> 00:07:46,720
Let's talk outside.

128
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:47,430
Let's go.

129
00:07:49,960 --> 00:07:50,680
Just leave.

130
00:07:52,280 --> 00:07:53,720
I'm not going with you.

131
00:07:55,440 --> 00:07:57,200
I'll end this my own way.

132
00:08:02,360 --> 00:08:02,940
Besides,

133
00:08:04,440 --> 00:08:05,970
I don't care about my money.

134
00:08:07,390 --> 00:08:09,450
But you must give Cheng Ken his money.

135
00:08:09,630 --> 00:08:10,690
I promised him that

136
00:08:10,840 --> 00:08:12,840
I would help cure Jiajia's illness.

137
00:08:13,220 --> 00:08:14,420
I have to keep my word.

138
00:08:25,700 --> 00:08:26,490
Xiaoya.

139
00:08:30,320 --> 00:08:32,559
Why don't you solve your issues first?

140
00:08:32,870 --> 00:08:34,270
I can just stay at a hotel.

141
00:08:35,080 --> 00:08:35,679
It's fine.

142
00:08:35,870 --> 00:08:36,650
There's something wrong with him.

143
00:08:36,650 --> 00:08:37,750
He's been moody.

144
00:08:37,770 --> 00:08:39,200
Maybe he's under too much pressure lately.

145
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:39,960
Waiter.

146
00:08:40,340 --> 00:08:40,960
We're ready to order.

147
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:42,440
-Have a seat.
-Okay. Wait a minute.

148
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:43,669
Let me tell you about the shipping first.

149
00:08:43,669 --> 00:08:44,670
It's very simple.

150
00:08:45,550 --> 00:08:46,210
Have a seat.

151
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:49,790
Is your face okay?

152
00:08:49,790 --> 00:08:50,790
I'm fine.

153
00:08:53,750 --> 00:08:54,720
Really.

154
00:08:59,150 --> 00:09:01,080
The garlic scapes are tough today.

155
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:02,720
What?

156
00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:03,920
Are you going to throw up?

157
00:09:03,920 --> 00:09:04,820
No. My back hurts.

158
00:09:04,820 --> 00:09:06,420
I'm going to put my head down.

159
00:09:15,730 --> 00:09:16,450
Nie.

160
00:09:20,070 --> 00:09:21,500
All three bags, right?

161
00:09:23,210 --> 00:09:24,210
Nothing special?

162
00:09:25,710 --> 00:09:26,080
Okay.

163
00:09:26,080 --> 00:09:26,510
Got it.

164
00:09:26,510 --> 00:09:27,200
Thanks.

165
00:09:29,270 --> 00:09:30,870
What did you ask Nie to check?

166
00:09:31,870 --> 00:09:32,270
Nothing.

167
00:09:32,270 --> 00:09:33,000
Diet pills.

168
00:09:37,310 --> 00:09:38,220
Just sleep.

169
00:09:38,360 --> 00:09:39,290
I'll keep watch.

170
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:40,550
I know.

171
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:54,580
I'm going away for a while.

172
00:09:56,910 --> 00:09:59,960
You'll stay at Great-Aunt's house
for now.

173
00:10:00,750 --> 00:10:02,750
If your uncle comes for you

174
00:10:02,750 --> 00:10:04,480
to take you away,

175
00:10:04,710 --> 00:10:05,920
just go with him.

176
00:10:06,860 --> 00:10:09,330
He'll take you to a new place to live.

177
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:11,670
After

178
00:10:12,260 --> 00:10:13,780
I finish my business,

179
00:10:14,140 --> 00:10:15,930
I'll find a way to get there
as soon as possible

180
00:10:15,930 --> 00:10:18,250
to meet up with you.

181
00:10:18,970 --> 00:10:21,490
We'll have a lot of money then.

182
00:10:22,050 --> 00:10:23,500
We can cure your illness.

183
00:10:27,690 --> 00:10:28,780
If

184
00:10:29,780 --> 00:10:31,940
you uncle and I suddenly disappear...

185
00:10:32,430 --> 00:10:34,640
Do you mean you are caught by the police?

186
00:10:39,890 --> 00:10:40,560
Yes.

187
00:10:41,560 --> 00:10:43,590
You'll see Uncle Jin Longzheng then.

188
00:10:43,590 --> 00:10:44,840
The police officer, Uncle Jin.

189
00:10:44,840 --> 00:10:45,640
Remember him?

190
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:47,720
Stick to him

191
00:10:48,050 --> 00:10:49,450
and let him take you away.

192
00:10:49,930 --> 00:10:50,810
He's a good man.

193
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:54,290
He'll do whatever it takes
to treat your illness.

194
00:10:54,290 --> 00:10:56,020
Then you'll be able to survive.

195
00:10:56,370 --> 00:10:58,130
What about Xiaoyu?

196
00:11:02,030 --> 00:11:04,460
We can't worry about her right now.

197
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:07,870
You promised me.

198
00:11:10,430 --> 00:11:12,040
I did promise you.

199
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:14,370
Jia.

200
00:11:14,390 --> 00:11:15,910
If you have to choose

201
00:11:16,310 --> 00:11:18,980
between Xiaoyu and me,

202
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:20,880
which one would you pick?

203
00:11:20,950 --> 00:11:22,640
I'd pick you, for sure.

204
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:24,520
But I don't want to make a choice.

205
00:11:30,530 --> 00:11:31,190
Okay.

206
00:11:31,780 --> 00:11:32,710
You don't have to.

207
00:11:32,710 --> 00:11:33,640
We're both here.

208
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:37,530
Go to sleep. Goodnight.

209
00:12:02,110 --> 00:12:03,820
He suffered for so many years.

210
00:12:08,770 --> 00:12:10,170
It's good that he's gone.

211
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:29,670
Jiang.

212
00:12:34,670 --> 00:12:36,790
Good boy.

213
00:12:39,510 --> 00:12:41,480
No more suffering.

214
00:12:43,480 --> 00:12:45,360
No more suffering.

215
00:13:03,830 --> 00:13:04,590
Mr. Xue.

216
00:13:05,390 --> 00:13:06,120
Cheng Ken.

217
00:13:09,560 --> 00:13:11,220
Bring Jiajia to the hospital.

218
00:13:12,990 --> 00:13:14,040
Jiang is gone.

219
00:13:15,080 --> 00:13:16,030
Jiajia.

220
00:13:16,270 --> 00:13:17,080
Wake up, Jiajia.

221
00:13:17,080 --> 00:13:18,340
Get up and get changed.

222
00:13:20,330 --> 00:13:20,940
Wenjing.

223
00:13:21,110 --> 00:13:22,920
Cheng Ken ran out with Jiajia.

224
00:13:24,550 --> 00:13:25,440
Copy that.

225
00:13:28,110 --> 00:13:29,080
I saw them.

226
00:14:15,680 --> 00:14:16,280
Director.

227
00:14:17,150 --> 00:14:17,670
Mr. Xue.

228
00:14:18,150 --> 00:14:18,800
Mrs. Xue.

229
00:14:21,080 --> 00:14:21,600
Jiajia.

230
00:14:21,790 --> 00:14:22,390
Come here.

231
00:14:22,410 --> 00:14:23,410
Kneel and kowtow.

232
00:14:24,200 --> 00:14:24,860
Kneel down.

233
00:14:24,930 --> 00:14:25,700
Kowtow.

234
00:14:27,440 --> 00:14:27,970
Kowtow.

235
00:14:30,210 --> 00:14:32,210
Call them Godfather and Godmother.

236
00:14:33,610 --> 00:14:35,610
Call them Godfather and Godmother.

237
00:14:35,800 --> 00:14:36,870
Godfather, Godmother.

238
00:14:36,870 --> 00:14:37,650
Louder.

239
00:14:37,750 --> 00:14:39,080
Godfather, Godmother.

240
00:14:40,200 --> 00:14:41,320
From now on, treat them

241
00:14:41,320 --> 00:14:43,440
as your own mom and dad.

242
00:14:43,840 --> 00:14:44,570
Understand?

243
00:14:48,330 --> 00:14:50,130
I have my reasons for doing this.

244
00:14:51,270 --> 00:14:52,530
I understand, Mr. Xue.

245
00:14:53,240 --> 00:14:54,460
You'll get every cent I promised.

246
00:14:54,460 --> 00:14:55,720
You don't understand!

247
00:14:56,380 --> 00:14:56,970
Xue.

248
00:14:57,600 --> 00:14:58,270
Calm down.

249
00:15:00,120 --> 00:15:01,510
Has Jiajia eaten anything after 8:00?

250
00:15:01,510 --> 00:15:02,240
No.

251
00:15:02,240 --> 00:15:03,030
Nothing at all.

252
00:15:03,030 --> 00:15:03,510
Remember,

253
00:15:03,510 --> 00:15:04,960
she can't eat anything from now on,

254
00:15:04,960 --> 00:15:06,060
not even a drop of water.

255
00:15:06,060 --> 00:15:07,150
Listen to the nurse for everything.

256
00:15:07,150 --> 00:15:08,750
Time is of the essence for
organ transplants.

257
00:15:08,750 --> 00:15:09,390
If conditions allow,

258
00:15:09,390 --> 00:15:10,200
we'll operate tomorrow morning.

259
00:15:10,200 --> 00:15:11,080
Okay.

260
00:15:11,170 --> 00:15:11,510
Hurry.

261
00:15:11,510 --> 00:15:12,630
Get up, Jia.

262
00:15:12,650 --> 00:15:13,370
Get up.

263
00:15:13,750 --> 00:15:14,270
Get up.

264
00:15:15,790 --> 00:15:17,510
The admission counters of
the outpatient and inpatient registration

265
00:15:17,510 --> 00:15:18,440
are closed now.

266
00:15:18,440 --> 00:15:19,150
I just spoke to them.

267
00:15:19,150 --> 00:15:20,270
Go pay the fees and handle the paperwork.

268
00:15:20,270 --> 00:15:21,080
Okay.

269
00:15:21,390 --> 00:15:22,320
Director.

270
00:15:22,480 --> 00:15:23,120
Well.

271
00:15:23,320 --> 00:15:24,240
What are you doing?

272
00:15:24,240 --> 00:15:25,150
Cheng Ken, what are you doing?

273
00:15:25,150 --> 00:15:26,000
Please.

274
00:15:26,000 --> 00:15:26,730
Take it back.

275
00:15:27,480 --> 00:15:29,390
Take Jia for the preoperative checkup.

276
00:15:29,390 --> 00:15:29,870
Thank you.

277
00:15:29,870 --> 00:15:31,070
Thank you, Director.

278
00:15:37,030 --> 00:15:38,150
My dear daughter.

279
00:15:38,320 --> 00:15:40,080
You'll be all better soon.

280
00:15:40,730 --> 00:15:41,930
You'll be well soon.

281
00:15:42,600 --> 00:15:45,320
Then you can go out and
play like other kids.

282
00:15:45,500 --> 00:15:46,630
You can go to school.

283
00:15:47,440 --> 00:15:49,550
Will I still need dialysis?

284
00:15:51,960 --> 00:15:52,960
To hell with that.

285
00:15:53,080 --> 00:15:53,870
Never again.

286
00:15:55,190 --> 00:15:55,910
No more.

287
00:15:58,550 --> 00:15:59,350
Smile for Dad.

288
00:15:59,720 --> 00:16:00,520
Smile for Dad.

289
00:16:17,460 --> 00:16:18,250
Go on.

290
00:16:38,050 --> 00:16:39,940
You are my family's savior.

291
00:16:42,890 --> 00:16:44,770
Stop acting.

292
00:16:45,720 --> 00:16:47,790
Get out. I don't want to see you.

293
00:16:51,990 --> 00:16:53,200
Go.

294
00:17:11,740 --> 00:17:15,540
[Nuanfeng County People's Hospital
Death Notice]

295
00:17:32,070 --> 00:17:33,110
One at a time.

296
00:17:36,110 --> 00:17:37,640
You only ate fried chicken?

297
00:17:37,640 --> 00:17:39,370
Grandpa only made this for you?

298
00:17:40,590 --> 00:17:42,110
Tell Grandpa to make it less often.

299
00:17:42,110 --> 00:17:44,440
Kids can't eat fried chicken frequently.

300
00:17:45,070 --> 00:17:45,820
What about homework?

301
00:17:45,820 --> 00:17:46,680
How is it going?

302
00:17:48,030 --> 00:17:49,070
Pay attention to your homework.

303
00:17:49,070 --> 00:17:50,800
I'll be back next week to check.

304
00:17:51,240 --> 00:17:52,550
Do not play on your iPad at night,

305
00:17:52,550 --> 00:17:54,110
especially not in the dark.

306
00:17:54,440 --> 00:17:55,500
Or you'll go blind.

307
00:17:57,200 --> 00:17:58,200
Alright, hang up now.

308
00:17:58,200 --> 00:17:59,460
I'll be back next week.

309
00:18:00,550 --> 00:18:01,810
No need to get Grandpa.

310
00:18:02,650 --> 00:18:03,270
Bye.

311
00:18:03,600 --> 00:18:04,200
Bye.

312
00:18:10,790 --> 00:18:11,400
What's up?

313
00:18:15,030 --> 00:18:16,480
Jiang is only nine.

314
00:18:17,720 --> 00:18:18,980
Do you believe in fate?

315
00:18:22,480 --> 00:18:23,240
I used to.

316
00:18:23,240 --> 00:18:23,880
But now...

317
00:18:24,160 --> 00:18:25,090
I don't anymore.

318
00:18:26,070 --> 00:18:26,750
Why?

319
00:18:27,750 --> 00:18:28,720
I just don't.

320
00:18:28,720 --> 00:18:29,750
There's no why.

321
00:18:32,430 --> 00:18:33,400
I saw you guys earlier.

322
00:18:33,400 --> 00:18:34,240
I didn't have time to say hi.

323
00:18:34,240 --> 00:18:35,170
Why are you here?

324
00:18:35,450 --> 00:18:36,250
Well.

325
00:18:36,310 --> 00:18:37,750
We have to be where you are.

326
00:18:37,750 --> 00:18:38,640
It's a tacit understanding.

327
00:18:38,640 --> 00:18:39,280
Right?

328
00:18:40,160 --> 00:18:41,290
Can you do me a favor?

329
00:18:41,680 --> 00:18:42,350
Jiajia is hospitalized.

330
00:18:42,350 --> 00:18:43,070
Please pay the fees for me.

331
00:18:43,070 --> 00:18:43,720
Here's the card.

332
00:18:43,720 --> 00:18:44,310
I have diarrhea.

333
00:18:44,310 --> 00:18:45,480
Give it to me.

334
00:18:45,500 --> 00:18:46,190
Thanks.

335
00:18:47,620 --> 00:18:48,550
The password is?

336
00:18:49,170 --> 00:18:50,500
Five eights and a seven.

337
00:19:04,390 --> 00:19:05,790
Do you have toilet paper?

338
00:19:05,940 --> 00:19:06,740
Yes.

339
00:19:12,680 --> 00:19:13,880
Our colleagues

340
00:19:13,880 --> 00:19:15,410
heard about your situation

341
00:19:15,750 --> 00:19:17,950
and wanted to chip in some money for you.

342
00:19:20,940 --> 00:19:22,090
Thanks to all of you.

343
00:19:56,830 --> 00:19:58,030
What happened to you?

344
00:19:58,250 --> 00:19:59,140
Cheng Ken!

345
00:19:59,830 --> 00:20:00,630
Cheng Ken!

346
00:20:02,210 --> 00:20:03,300
Call a doctor!

347
00:20:05,230 --> 00:20:06,510
Hold on.

348
00:20:09,110 --> 00:20:10,350
Doctor!

349
00:20:10,370 --> 00:20:11,170
Nurse!

350
00:20:11,240 --> 00:20:13,100
Someone fainted in the restroom.

351
00:20:13,740 --> 00:20:14,240
What happened?

352
00:20:14,240 --> 00:20:16,170
Cheng Ken fainted in the restroom.

353
00:20:29,310 --> 00:20:30,570
Wait, he was just here.

354
00:20:31,110 --> 00:20:31,800
He was just here, right?

355
00:20:31,800 --> 00:20:32,230
Yes.

356
00:20:32,680 --> 00:20:33,340
Right here.

357
00:20:39,580 --> 00:20:40,510
Is anyone there?

358
00:20:41,110 --> 00:20:41,790
Cheng Ken?

359
00:22:56,240 --> 00:22:56,830
Sorry.

360
00:22:57,030 --> 00:22:59,150
The subscriber you dialed is powered off.

361
00:22:59,150 --> 00:22:59,870
Sorry.

362
00:23:00,070 --> 00:23:01,730
The subscriber you dialed...

363
00:23:07,240 --> 00:23:07,830
Sorry.

364
00:23:08,030 --> 00:23:10,360
The subscriber you dialed is powered off.

365
00:23:33,520 --> 00:23:34,240
It's me.

366
00:23:35,610 --> 00:23:36,930
Can I leave a day early?

367
00:23:37,080 --> 00:23:37,950
I can pay extra.

368
00:23:38,830 --> 00:23:40,030
When is the earliest?

369
00:23:41,310 --> 00:23:42,030
Okay.

370
00:23:42,550 --> 00:23:44,010
Tomorrow afternoon then.

371
00:23:44,510 --> 00:23:46,040
Just wait for me at the pier.

372
00:24:03,750 --> 00:24:04,710
Why are you here?

373
00:24:06,160 --> 00:24:08,020
Xiaodong didn't answer my calls.

374
00:24:08,030 --> 00:24:09,750
You can't come here!

375
00:24:10,720 --> 00:24:12,250
The police will follow you.

376
00:24:14,440 --> 00:24:15,840
Xiaoya, I need money now.

377
00:24:17,240 --> 00:24:18,790
Didn't I say I'd give it to you
in a few days?

378
00:24:18,790 --> 00:24:19,830
I can't wait.

379
00:24:20,240 --> 00:24:21,750
Jiajia is already in the hospital.

380
00:24:21,750 --> 00:24:22,960
The surgery will start tomorrow morning.

381
00:24:22,960 --> 00:24:24,690
I promised them a million yuan.

382
00:24:25,020 --> 00:24:25,950
Once you get out,

383
00:24:25,970 --> 00:24:27,000
everything will be fine.

384
00:24:27,000 --> 00:24:28,030
Why does it have to be now?

385
00:24:28,030 --> 00:24:29,160
There's a kidney available right now.

386
00:24:29,160 --> 00:24:30,240
Why should I wait to go abroad?

387
00:24:30,240 --> 00:24:31,900
Does it really cost that much?

388
00:24:31,960 --> 00:24:32,720
You're giving them a million?

389
00:24:32,720 --> 00:24:33,520
Are you crazy?

390
00:24:33,860 --> 00:24:35,290
It is my business.

391
00:24:35,880 --> 00:24:37,070
I deserve far more than a million.

392
00:24:37,070 --> 00:24:37,550
Right?

393
00:24:38,270 --> 00:24:39,340
If I transfer the money to you now,

394
00:24:39,340 --> 00:24:40,490
within ten minutes,

395
00:24:40,520 --> 00:24:41,850
the police will be here.

396
00:24:43,410 --> 00:24:44,520
Then give me cash.

397
00:24:45,190 --> 00:24:45,870
Ken,

398
00:24:46,200 --> 00:24:47,890
where am I supposed to get cash this late?

399
00:24:47,890 --> 00:24:48,920
Tomorrow morning,

400
00:24:48,920 --> 00:24:50,840
go to the bank and get me the cash.

401
00:24:51,400 --> 00:24:53,400
I need to make an appointment
for large withdrawals.

402
00:24:53,400 --> 00:24:55,400
I don't care. That's your business.

403
00:24:56,190 --> 00:24:58,520
If I don't get the money
by 9 a.m. tomorrow,

404
00:24:58,570 --> 00:24:59,700
I'll turn myself in.

405
00:25:07,860 --> 00:25:09,190
Are you threatening me?

406
00:25:11,020 --> 00:25:12,740
Believe it or not, tonight,

407
00:25:13,810 --> 00:25:15,210
I can make you disappear.

408
00:25:35,370 --> 00:25:36,430
What are you doing?

409
00:25:36,880 --> 00:25:38,210
Are you out of your mind?

410
00:25:43,530 --> 00:25:44,380
Cheng Ken.

411
00:25:45,710 --> 00:25:46,560
Officer Jin.

412
00:25:47,910 --> 00:25:48,400
Cheng Ken,

413
00:25:48,400 --> 00:25:49,730
where are you right now?

414
00:25:51,350 --> 00:25:52,060
Cheng Ken.

415
00:25:55,750 --> 00:25:57,290
Jiajia's admission procedures are done.

416
00:25:57,290 --> 00:25:58,080
Where are you?

417
00:25:58,080 --> 00:26:00,340
When are you coming back to the hospital?

418
00:26:07,810 --> 00:26:08,680
Cheng Ken.

419
00:26:11,600 --> 00:26:12,640
What?

420
00:26:13,590 --> 00:26:14,480
I don't know.

421
00:26:14,480 --> 00:26:15,740
Let me try calling him.

422
00:26:23,800 --> 00:26:25,400
Tomorrow at 9 a.m.,

423
00:26:27,070 --> 00:26:28,170
meet me at Shenmao Bank,

424
00:26:28,170 --> 00:26:29,170
Jinbao Street.

425
00:26:50,120 --> 00:26:51,050
His phone is off.

426
00:26:52,440 --> 00:26:53,570
What does this mean?

427
00:26:53,960 --> 00:26:54,590
Where is he now?

428
00:26:54,590 --> 00:26:56,350
Why did he call me?

429
00:27:00,000 --> 00:27:01,550
Look, at this critical moment,

430
00:27:01,550 --> 00:27:03,440
his kid is about to have surgery.

431
00:27:04,800 --> 00:27:05,790
What could he be doing?

432
00:27:05,790 --> 00:27:06,960
He must be going to get...

433
00:27:06,960 --> 00:27:07,580
Money.

434
00:27:07,650 --> 00:27:08,590
Right, he wants money.

435
00:27:08,590 --> 00:27:09,650
He needs money now.

436
00:27:10,790 --> 00:27:13,250
Xue agreed to give Jiang's kidney
to Jiajia.

437
00:27:14,020 --> 00:27:15,440
Cheng Ken must have promised

438
00:27:15,440 --> 00:27:16,840
to give Xue a sum of money.

439
00:27:18,240 --> 00:27:19,310
Look, let's think this through.

440
00:27:19,310 --> 00:27:21,590
Cheng Ken knows we're tracking him now,

441
00:27:21,590 --> 00:27:22,000
right?

442
00:27:24,560 --> 00:27:26,090
He's out looking for money.

443
00:27:26,310 --> 00:27:27,590
There are only two ways for him to get it.

444
00:27:27,590 --> 00:27:29,820
If he already got the drug money

445
00:27:29,850 --> 00:27:30,830
and hid it somewhere,

446
00:27:30,830 --> 00:27:31,900
maybe he is going to retrieve it now.

447
00:27:31,900 --> 00:27:33,930
Or he's going to meet his accomplices

448
00:27:33,930 --> 00:27:35,810
for money

449
00:27:35,840 --> 00:27:36,810
if he didn't get it before.

450
00:27:36,810 --> 00:27:38,940
These are his only two options, right?

451
00:27:40,880 --> 00:27:41,550
Yes.

452
00:27:42,070 --> 00:27:43,110
It's fine. If we can't find him today,

453
00:27:43,110 --> 00:27:44,770
we can go wait at the hospital.

454
00:27:44,790 --> 00:27:46,140
Jiajia is having surgery soon.

455
00:27:46,140 --> 00:27:47,400
Where else would he go?

456
00:27:48,240 --> 00:27:49,300
He has to come back.

457
00:27:51,550 --> 00:27:53,200
What the hell is he doing?

458
00:28:15,650 --> 00:28:16,930
Don't leave tonight.

459
00:28:17,510 --> 00:28:18,160
No.

460
00:28:18,160 --> 00:28:19,760
I just transferred the shop.

461
00:28:19,850 --> 00:28:21,250
I have to go back and pack.

462
00:28:22,100 --> 00:28:23,180
Go to bed early.

463
00:28:24,070 --> 00:28:24,680
Mom.

464
00:28:28,920 --> 00:28:29,990
Come here. Hug me.

465
00:28:38,350 --> 00:28:39,610
You have a bad stomach.

466
00:28:39,960 --> 00:28:41,290
Remember to eat on time.

467
00:28:43,320 --> 00:28:43,910
And

468
00:28:45,000 --> 00:28:46,480
don't always stay at home.

469
00:28:46,750 --> 00:28:48,410
Go square dance or something.

470
00:28:48,440 --> 00:28:49,230
Exercise more.

471
00:28:49,230 --> 00:28:50,370
All right, all right.

472
00:28:50,370 --> 00:28:51,700
Stop worrying about me.

473
00:28:55,680 --> 00:28:56,140
I'm off.

474
00:28:59,070 --> 00:29:00,310
Don't get too tired.

475
00:29:00,410 --> 00:29:01,370
Remember to eat.

476
00:29:09,350 --> 00:29:11,680
Find yourself a partner if you get lonely.

477
00:29:13,020 --> 00:29:13,980
Nonsense.

478
00:30:02,950 --> 00:30:03,680
Cheng Ken...

479
00:30:03,880 --> 00:30:05,410
Cheng Ken is out of control.

480
00:30:06,030 --> 00:30:06,790
Xiaodong,

481
00:30:07,100 --> 00:30:08,560
I didn't mean to lie to you.

482
00:30:08,790 --> 00:30:10,070
I just wanted an extra safeguard.

483
00:30:10,070 --> 00:30:11,000
Believe me.

484
00:30:11,960 --> 00:30:12,930
I have

485
00:30:13,230 --> 00:30:14,830
moved up our departure date.

486
00:30:15,020 --> 00:30:16,420
We're leaving tomorrow.

487
00:30:17,940 --> 00:30:19,070
If you still love me,

488
00:30:20,000 --> 00:30:21,000
tomorrow morning

489
00:30:21,230 --> 00:30:21,990
at 8:30,

490
00:30:22,880 --> 00:30:23,880
on Jinbao Street,

491
00:30:24,060 --> 00:30:26,260
meet me at the entrance of Shenmao Bank.

492
00:30:26,400 --> 00:30:27,000
Okay?

493
00:31:16,310 --> 00:31:16,840
I will...

494
00:31:16,880 --> 00:31:17,550
Don't move.

495
00:31:17,650 --> 00:31:18,850
I'm clearing a level.

496
00:32:14,770 --> 00:32:15,960
The interrogation data you submitted today

497
00:32:15,960 --> 00:32:16,980
has something wrong.

498
00:32:16,980 --> 00:32:19,110
Don't leave tonight unless you fix it.

499
00:32:53,060 --> 00:32:54,390
Temperature is normal.

500
00:33:00,160 --> 00:33:01,350
After 10 o'clock tonight,

501
00:33:01,350 --> 00:33:02,680
you can't eat or drink.

502
00:33:02,700 --> 00:33:04,230
Don't be nervous tomorrow.

503
00:33:04,480 --> 00:33:06,750
A nurse from the operating room
will come for you.

504
00:33:06,750 --> 00:33:07,440
Then,

505
00:33:07,640 --> 00:33:09,240
once you get out of surgery,

506
00:33:09,240 --> 00:33:10,840
you'll be alive and kicking.

507
00:33:10,990 --> 00:33:13,450
Press the bedside bell
if you need anything.

508
00:34:29,540 --> 00:34:30,600
You came after all.

509
00:34:33,260 --> 00:34:34,320
Where is Cheng Ken?

510
00:34:36,480 --> 00:34:39,340
I agreed to meet him at 9 o'clock
to pick up the money.

511
00:34:40,730 --> 00:34:41,929
How much does he want?

512
00:34:42,590 --> 00:34:43,280
A million.

513
00:34:44,949 --> 00:34:47,350
Isn't all your money in overseas accounts?

514
00:34:47,600 --> 00:34:49,000
A sum arrived yesterday.

515
00:34:49,560 --> 00:34:51,489
I asked President Zhou for a favor.

516
00:34:51,510 --> 00:34:53,170
They will start work at eight.

517
00:34:53,440 --> 00:34:54,110
By nine,

518
00:34:54,590 --> 00:34:55,719
we can get the money.

519
00:34:56,989 --> 00:34:58,200
President Zhou

520
00:34:59,110 --> 00:35:00,570
barely has to lift a finger

521
00:35:00,960 --> 00:35:02,290
to get a ten percent cut.

522
00:35:03,200 --> 00:35:04,680
It's the least he can do.

523
00:35:06,630 --> 00:35:07,960
Then why did you call me?

524
00:35:12,280 --> 00:35:12,920
Go with me.

525
00:35:15,030 --> 00:35:16,160
At 2 this afternoon,

526
00:35:16,880 --> 00:35:18,410
the boat will be at the pier.

527
00:35:20,960 --> 00:35:23,710
When Cheng Ken takes over a million yuan
to the hospital,

528
00:35:23,710 --> 00:35:24,790
by 10:30,

529
00:35:25,070 --> 00:35:27,200
the police will figure out
we're his accomplices.

530
00:35:27,200 --> 00:35:27,980
We won't be able to leave.

531
00:35:27,980 --> 00:35:29,270
They have no evidence.

532
00:35:29,520 --> 00:35:31,150
The goods at home are all fake.

533
00:35:31,150 --> 00:35:33,240
Even if Hu Wenjing finds the goods,

534
00:35:33,710 --> 00:35:34,960
inspection and testing

535
00:35:34,960 --> 00:35:36,310
will take more than four hours.

536
00:35:36,310 --> 00:35:38,710
By then, we'll be in international waters.

537
00:35:41,320 --> 00:35:42,380
What about Xiaoyu?

538
00:35:42,770 --> 00:35:44,300
Xiaoyu is in your hometown.

539
00:35:44,530 --> 00:35:47,130
It won't take the police four hours
to find her.

540
00:36:00,000 --> 00:36:01,800
I should have been ruthless then

541
00:36:02,320 --> 00:36:03,320
and killed her.

542
00:36:09,280 --> 00:36:10,680
We can't leave together.

543
00:36:10,870 --> 00:36:11,600
You go first.

544
00:36:12,410 --> 00:36:13,890
I'll handle the rest.

545
00:36:24,800 --> 00:36:25,590
You will die.

546
00:36:29,760 --> 00:36:30,720
If I die,

547
00:36:30,760 --> 00:36:32,040
would you really care?

548
00:36:48,130 --> 00:36:49,660
As long as Xiaoyu is killed,

549
00:36:50,570 --> 00:36:52,170
maybe we still have a chance.

550
00:36:59,030 --> 00:37:00,070
After I get out,

551
00:37:01,760 --> 00:37:02,800
you can push everything

552
00:37:02,800 --> 00:37:03,960
onto me.

553
00:37:04,260 --> 00:37:05,570
You can tell them that everything

554
00:37:05,570 --> 00:37:06,450
was done by me,

555
00:37:07,770 --> 00:37:09,430
and you didn't know anything.

556
00:37:10,030 --> 00:37:11,160
But as for Cheng Ken,

557
00:37:12,110 --> 00:37:13,510
he knows too much.

558
00:37:13,760 --> 00:37:14,440
Once the police catch him...

559
00:37:14,440 --> 00:37:15,550
Don't worry about it.

560
00:37:15,550 --> 00:37:16,880
After leaving the bank,

561
00:37:17,000 --> 00:37:18,440
go to the pier and wait for the boat.

562
00:37:18,440 --> 00:37:19,960
I'll handle the rest.

563
00:37:31,350 --> 00:37:32,550
What time can I get the money?

564
00:37:32,550 --> 00:37:33,150
Just wait.

565
00:37:39,190 --> 00:37:40,230
1.08 million.

566
00:37:41,120 --> 00:37:43,230
This is the cut from the first payment.

567
00:37:43,230 --> 00:37:44,360
The rest of the money

568
00:37:44,730 --> 00:37:46,390
will be given to you as agreed.

569
00:37:46,500 --> 00:37:47,230
Then we...

570
00:37:47,250 --> 00:37:48,850
Xiaodong, you guys go first.

571
00:37:56,550 --> 00:37:57,240
Mr. Zhou,

572
00:37:57,840 --> 00:37:59,040
sorry to trouble you.

573
00:38:00,230 --> 00:38:01,400
I'd also like to discuss

574
00:38:01,400 --> 00:38:03,640
the future funds in my account.

575
00:38:13,920 --> 00:38:15,780
What's the situation on your end?

576
00:38:17,050 --> 00:38:18,220
Anything unusual?

577
00:38:21,440 --> 00:38:22,700
Nothing unusual here.

578
00:38:22,900 --> 00:38:23,820
Mr. Xue said

579
00:38:23,880 --> 00:38:25,140
Cheng Ken promised him

580
00:38:25,150 --> 00:38:26,500
to be back this morning.

581
00:38:41,090 --> 00:38:43,010
